==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: off-the-cuff
<hw>off-the-cuff</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>with little or no preparation
or forethought; unrehearsed; extemporaneous; offhand.</def> <illu>his
<ex>off-the-cuff</ex> remarks offended many people</illu>; <illu>an
<ex>off-the-cuff</ex> toast</illu>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ad-lib, extemporaneous, extemporary, extempore,
offhand, offhanded, unpremeditated, unrehearsed.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>off the hook</ent>⟦br⟧
